
- create a release branch
- bump version (setup.py, bowser.json and package.json)
- build newest englisch translations (django + djangojs)
- push translations
- pull translations
- compile translations
- run tests and recreate test env

- update freeze on develop branch
- update bower libs on develop branch

- pypi:
  Remove old build directory
  python setup.py register
  python setup.py bdist_wheel upload
  python setup.py sdist upload
